---
title: Crispy Chickpea Bowl with Israeli Couscous and Roasted Herbed Veggies
description: While we love chickpeas in any form, we have to admit: when roasted, they’re pretty spectacular. In this dish, crispy chickpeas meet nutty toasted couscous, creamy feta, and a whole slew of veggies. We only use half the chickpeas, but leftovers make an amazing snack!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/be-israeli-couscous-salad-4557f30f.jpg
